'''二溴化铬'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，[[化学式|化学式]] CrBr<sub>2</sub>.

==制备==
[[溴化铬|CrBr<sub>3</sub>]]会被还原为 CrBr<sub>2</sub>。具体方法是把 CrBr<sub>3</sub> 和[[氢气|氢气]]在350-400 °C的温度反应 6–10 个小时，会生成 CrBr<sub>2</sub> 和[[溴化氢|溴化氢]]。<ref name="German">{{cite book|last=Brauer|first=Georg|date=1965|origyear=1962|title=Handbuch Der Präparativen Anorganischen Chemie|trans-title=Handbook of Preparative Inorganic Chemistry|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Pef47TK5NfkC|language=de|volume=2|location=Stuttgart; New York, New York|publisher=Ferdinand Enke Verlag; Academic Press, Inc.|page=1341|isbn=978-0-32316129-9|accessdate=2014-01-10|archive-date=2020-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200729173436/https://books.google.com/books?id=Pef47TK5NfkC|dead-url=no}}</ref>

